{"type": "article", "id": 26402, "title": "世界上最小的无人机", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-05T07:08:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 71, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133422t43pNmSBIneYzf1a.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">由 <a href=\"https://www.trndlabs.com/\">TRNDlabs</a> 设计的世界上最小的无人机来了：虽然 SKEYE Pico （暂时还）没有拍摄功能，但它胜在大小（长宽均为 2.2 厘米），甚至可以直接放进它的控制器里随身携带。它共有三种操作模式，即便你是第一次操作也能轻松上手（对于渴望挑战的老手，Headless 模式是为你们准备的）。你可以在<a href=\"https://www.trndlabs.com/product/skeye-pico-drone/\">链接</a>中看到它的详细规格，售价为 49 美元。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133420HzdXFp7Tgk3ZUK19.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133420ghfv8YwPybB5Z0Fj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133421ePKuXO3jfwGqUsZg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021334213C7SbLauf8YWANi6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}